*Bogati* ljudi imaju puno novca. (Rich people have a lot of money.)

Oni su *bogatili* sebe kroz godine. (They have enriched themselves over the years.)

Oni su *bogatstvo* stekli na nezakonit način. (They gained wealth in an unlawful manner.)

Oni su se *bogatili* radeći puno. (They got rich by working hard.)

Neke porodice su *bogati* od pokoljenja do pokoljenja. (Some families have been wealthy from generation to generation.)